7.0 WINNINGS, PAYOUTS & PROFIT DISTRIBUTION 

 
 

On the Decent.bet platform, users will be able to buy DBET house credits for each 

session, a 3-month period. At the beginning of session 0 or the final week of any other 

session, users will be able to buy-in to the house by using DBETs to purchase DBET 

house credits. This essentially locks users‚Äô DBETs into the house and allows it to be 

redeemed only at the end of a session, along with profits. 

 

DBET house credits will also be exchanged on the DBET house exchange in the future 

for DBETs anytime during a session thereby providing liquidity. DBET house credits 

can also be rolled over to the next session in the final week of the current session, 

locking in a users‚Äô DBETs for another session while allowing them to redeem profits.  

 

Since smart contracts cannot automatically liquidate all DBET house credit holder‚Äôs 

due to its nature, at the beginning of every session following S1, DBET house credit 

holder‚Äôs will have to manually exchange their house credits to redeem their payouts. 

All DBET house credit holders will be notified through the front-end and via e-mail 

before each house credit buying period and at the beginning of every profit distribution 

period. 

 

Profits for a user during each session are calculated using the following equation -  

 

