not exceed $50,000.00 per session donation. 

 

The focus of the charity will be to provide support for humanity worldwide.  The 

beneficiaries of the charity will be chosen in 2 ways, by the founders and by a vote 

through the community. 

 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 
 

